version of perl scripts and also Dockerfile. to make the image with
all resources, vcf2maf and vep.
currently it is v1.0 on docker hub. 

the docker-compose.yml is not supposed to work here. need to specify 
the input and ref (cache vep) in the working folder.
SNS101Seq/Data/mutation!!!!
also it is supposed to work with snakemake (not necessarily)

